title: Twitch’s Relationship With Its Streamers Shows Its Cracks
description: The service recently said it was going to take a bigger cut of the money it shared with streamers. At an annual gathering in San Diego, they vented about the decision.

title: Who Gets the Last Word on Steve Jobs? He Might.
description: When Laurene Powell Jobs unveiled a website dedicated to the story of her late husband, historians wondered if it could change how influential people burnish their legacies.
